<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Pretest Quiz</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .quiz-container {
            width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .question {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .options label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #1a73e8;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #1558b0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="quiz-container">
    <form>

        <div class="question">
            <h2>1. In a blanking operation, the piece removed is considered?</h2>
            <div class="options">
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1"> a: Scrap</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1"> b: The useful part</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1"> c: Waste material</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1"> d: None of the above</label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="question">
            <h2>2. The clearance in a shearing operation is the distance between?</h2>
            <div class="options">
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2"> a: Punch and Stripper</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2"> b: Punch cutting edge and Die cutting edge</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2"> c: Die and Stripper</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2"> d: Upper and Lower Die shoes</label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="question">
            <h2>3. Cutting force is directly proportional to?</h2>
            <div class="options">
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3"> a: Sheet Area</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3"> b: Sheet Thickness</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3"> c: Modulus of Elasticity</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3"> d: Poisson's Ratio</label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="question">
            <h2>4. Which stage comes first in the shearing process?</h2>
            <div class="options">
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4"> a: Fracture</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4"> b: Plastic Deformation</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4"> c: Penetration</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4"> d: Elastic Recovery</label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="question">
            <h2>5. Excessive clearance results in?</h2>
            <div class="options">
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5"> a: Cleaner cuts</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5"> b: Reduced force</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5"> c: Formation of burrs</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5"> d: Tool breakage</label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Submit Quiz</button>

    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>
